Hackathon - _________ is an event organized by Bce Bakhtiyarpur, that lasts for

2-3 days and the students participate in a team of 1 to 5 like-minded individuals to utilize new technologies and hack together tons of code from different sources to achieve their goal. Not only do programmers get the satisfaction of creating a useful product during the hackathon, but once the time runs out all participants come together and present their creations to a panel of judges who then give points based on the idea, execution, and presentation.

It is a glorious stage for sharing tech-related products and services among some of the best technical minds across the world, all with a common goal - to advance our technology to the NEXT LEVEL. With coverage from countless social media accounts, technical forums, and blogs, it is a massive opportunity for interaction with some of the brightest young minds and its impact is truly endless.

The second wave of Pandemic is again on our doors to capture our dreams, But this time we are also prepared to give it a good taste of medicine.

But ,With our hopes high and belt tight we have come up with , a hackathon conducted by AVYUKT `21, the annual Cultural- Techfest of Bce Bakhtiyapur . Many of the things are closed now, from the educational institutions to the multinational companies, and these are times when we are in much more need of a solution to problems which we encounter daily. With real life related themes we are very much happy to announce that in this hackathon we have included a plethora of themes, so choose the one which suits you and grab your coffee for this hackathon .

CHALLENGES

HealthCare

The world is reeling through one of the worst pandemics in the last century. These have raised many questions and have also forced us to modify the way we live. Not only the current scenario, but the post-covid world will also be markedly different from the pre- covid

world. Smart solutions for healthcare are the call of the hour.

Cloud computing

Cloud computing has been one of the trending topics in the modern developed world. Cloud computing has revolutionized the operations and existing techniques

to a great extent. And we think in the dire age of advancement we must contribute a bit by

accepting the projects in this field also.

Education

Education, whether formal or informal, can shape an individual's

life, both in the classroom and outside of it. The best way is to implement it in practical social life. So, in this hackathon, we really

wish to see some projects that will improve the quality of education in our society.

Open innovation

It is basically an alternative to this

conventional method of doing innovation where information has to stay within preset confines. A mindset, if you will, of being open to sharing and receiving information. Here, we will be pleased to get new ideas from our participants.

ML/AI

Today, with the power of Machine Learning and AI we can put computers to work on anything that we want them to do. Together lets get ready for the ML/AI evolutionand shape its projectsin a meaningful way, in

terms of technology, oversight, economics, and morality

Game Development

Game Development is the art of creating games and describes the design, development and release of a game. It may involve concept

generation, design, build, test and release. While you create a game, it is important to think about the game mechanics, rewards, player engagement and level design.

JUDGING CRITERIA FOR HACKATHON ::--

The Jury will evaluate the projects on the following criterion:

Uniqueness of the project - This criterion will be used to judge the projects using the existing solutions and how they are different from them .

Technology - Engineering skills demonstrated, quality of code, etc.

Practicality - Functionality and usefulness of the project in real life .

Sustainability - Has the team given a proper outlook of their plan of sustaining this project in the coming future?

Market Opportunity - How the idea will perform in the real world compared to its competitors and the future plan for the idea.

The participant will also have to demonstrate their working prototype of the project to the Jury members along with a presentation whose format will be forwarded.

If you have any queries regarding the project submission you can ask your questions on the channel official discord channel of Avyukyt .
